Let's all sing along to my holiday wishlist...

On the second day of Christmas, a Net54er sold to me… a Bergen (catching) Sov 460

On the third day of Christmas, a Net54er sold to me… a Burch (fielding) EPDG

On the fourth day of Christmas, a Net54er sold to me… a Burch (fielding) Old Mill

On the fifth day of Christmas, a Net54er sold to me… annn-yyy Brooklyn Carolina Brights

On the sixth day of Christmas, a Net54er sold to me… a Tim Jordan (portrait) EPDG

On the seventh day of Christmas, a Net54er sold to me… a Tim Jordan (batting) Old Mill

On the eighth day of Christmas, a Net54er sold to me… a Lennox Cycle 350

On the ninth day of Christmas, a Net54er sold to me… a McIntyre (Brooklyn) Sov 150

On the tenth day of Christmas, a Net54er sold to me… a Pastorius Sov 150

On the eleventh day of Christmas, a Net54er sold to me… a Rucker (portrait) EPDG

On the twelfth day of Christmas, a Net54er sold to me… a Wilhelm (batting) American Beauty
Santa Claus is here with a Tim Jordan Batting Old Mill.  Sending PM
